fields.description: Yoga mats made from 100% recyclable TPE and hypoallergenic materials. fields.name: Jade Yoga Harmony Yoga Mat
fields.description: Great Grip - open cell natural rubber provides optimum grip. Comfortable - natural rubber has more resilience and cushion. Through its partnership with Trees for the Future, JadeYoga plants a Tree with every mat sold. Made in the US with natural rubber, a renewable resource and contains no synthetic plastics.

fields.name: Manduka eKO Superlight Travel Yoga Mat
fields.description: Folds to fit in any travel bag or purse. Surface texture offers superior grip, even with light perspiration. Tightly woven scrim resists tearing or stretching. Closed cell design will not absorb bacteria. Made from non-Amazon harvested, natural tree rubber. No PVC, toxic plasticizers or harmful dyes.

fields.name: Yogibato Yoga Block Cork
fields.description: Yogibato cork blocks offer great support, especially when learning new asanas. The material is easy to grip and ensures secure hold even during strenuous yoga exercises.

fields.name: Myga Foam Yoga Block

fields.name: Leewadee Long Yoga Bolster
fields.description: Comfortable, stable and breathable thanks to the use of natural plant materials. Perfect for your meditative hours. Not a foam cushion, but all natural materials! Supporting for lower back, knees, legs, feet.

fields.name: Present Mind Yoga Bolster Roll
fields.description: Perfect support - the yoga bolster from Present Mind can help you maintain balance and ensures comfort during exercises. Washable cotton cover - owing to the robust zip placed along the entire width of the bolster, you can remove the cover, machine wash it and easily put it on again.
